INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2018-03-06 10:03:07','2018-03-06 10:03:07','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2018-03-06 10:03:07','2018-03-06 10:03:07','',0,'http:/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2018-03-06 10:03:07','2018-03-06 10:03:07','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http:/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','publish','closed','open','','sample-page','','','2018-03-06 10:03:07','2018-03-06 10:03:07','',0,'http:/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(22,1,'2018-04-08 22:17:24','2018-04-08 22:17:24','','Espresso','','inherit','open','closed','','espresso','','','2018-04-08 22:17:24','2018-04-08 22:17:24','',0,'http://18.219.193.133/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/espresso-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(23,1,'2018-04-08 22:17:24','2018-04-08 22:17:24','','Sandwich','','inherit','open','closed','','sandwich','','','2018-04-08 22:17:24','2018-04-08 22:17:24','',0,'http://18.219.193.133/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/sandwich-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(24,1,'2018-04-08 22:17:24','2018-04-08 22:17:24','','Coffee','','inherit','open','closed','','coffee','','','2018-04-08 22:17:24','2018-04-08 22:17:24','',0,'http://18.219.193.133/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/coffee-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(25,1,'2018-04-08 22:17:24','2018-04-08 22:17:24','Inspired by progressive legislation such as the standing order to expand Naloxone access to everyone.\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"100%\"><img src=\"http://naloxoneexchange.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Surgeon-General-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-235\" />\r\nThe first advisory warning in over a decade was recently issued by the Surgeon General, urging Americans to carry Naloxone, the drug that can stop opioid overdose.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"100%\"><img src=\"http://naloxoneexchange.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Screenshot_20180514-215309.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1187\" height=\"669\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-230\" />\r\nAt the current rate, the opioid epidemic will claim 500,000 lives in the next 10 years. Naloxone is a medication that can rapidly reverse opioid overdose and prevent overdose death. Naloxone Exchange is a HIPAA compliant online marketplace where you can purchase Naloxone without a prescription and have it shipped straight to your door!</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>','Naloxone Exchange','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2018-05-15 05:28:09','2018-05-15 05:28:09','',0,'http://18.219.193.133/?page_id=25',0,'page','',0),(26,1,'2018-04-08 22:17:24','2018-04-08 22:17:24','<img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-34\" src=\"http://18.219.193.133/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/Header_image-300x220.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"220\" />In 2016 over 60,000 people died of drug overdose due to opioid-related substances. The Naloxone Exchange, a company of <a href=\"http://www.fiduscript.com/\">Fiduscript</a>, is an online marketplace where you can purchase Naloxone 